description:
This endpoint will return aircraft data within the given radius (NM) of the provided points.

Get aircraft within 50 nautical miles of San Francisco, and within 20 nautical miles from New York (KJFK) at altitudes between 5000 and 30000 feet:
```
POST /api/aircraft/v2/proximity/radius
{
    "filters": [
        {
            "latitude": 37.7749,
            "longitude": -122.4194,
            "radius": 50
        },
        {
            "latitude": 40.641,
            "longitude": -73.775,
            "radius": 20,
            "altitude_min": 5000,
            "altitude_max": 30000
        },
        ...
    ]
}
```
